          "block_content": "TheFederal TradeCommission(FTC)is the agencyoftheU.S.governmentthat promotes free and fair trade competition. TheBureauof Consumer Protectionsafeguards consumers against unfair, deceptive,or fraudulent practices.Bothorganizations investigateviolations of federal consumer protection law.",
